001package edu.cnm.deepdive.appstarter.model.entity;
002
003import androidx.annotation.NonNull;
004import androidx.room.ColumnInfo;
005import androidx.room.Entity;
006import androidx.room.ForeignKey;
007import androidx.room.Index;
008import androidx.room.PrimaryKey;
009import java.time.Instant;
010
011
012@Entity(
013    tableName = "preset",
014    indices = {
015        @Index(value = "preset_name", unique = true)
016    }
017
018)
019public class Preset {
020    @PrimaryKey(autoGenerate = true)
021    @ColumnInfo(name = "preset_id")
022    private long id;
023    @ColumnInfo(name = "user_id")
024    private long userId;
025    @ColumnInfo(name = "preset_name")
026    private String presetName;
027    @ColumnInfo(name = "filter_position")
028    private float filterPosition;
029    @ColumnInfo(name = "spread_ribbon_position")
030    private float spreadRibbonPosition;
031    @ColumnInfo(name = "waveform_selection")
032    private float waveFormSelection;
033
034    @ColumnInfo(name = "noiseamount")
035    private float noiseAmount;
036    @NonNull
037    private Instant created = Instant.MIN;
038
039    @NonNull
040    public Instant getCreated() {
041        return created;
042    }
043
044    public long getId() {
045        return id;
046    }
047
048    public void setCreated(@NonNull Instant created) {
049        this.created = created;
050    }
051
052    public void setId(long id) {
053        this.id = id;
054    }
055
056    public long getUserId() {
057        return userId;
058    }
059
060    public void setUserId(long userId) {
061        this.userId = userId;
062    }
063
064    public String getPresetName() {
065        return presetName;
066    }
067
068    public void setPresetName(String presetName) {
069        this.presetName = presetName;
070    }
071
072    public float getFilterPosition() {
073        return filterPosition;
074    }
075
076    public void setFilterPosition(float filterPosition) {
077        this.filterPosition = filterPosition;
078    }
079
080    public float getSpreadKnobPosition() {
081        return spreadRibbonPosition;
082    }
083
084    public void setSpreadKnobPosition(float spreadKnobPosition) {
085        this.spreadRibbonPosition = spreadKnobPosition;
086    }
087
088    public float getWaveFormSelection() {
089        return waveFormSelection;
090    }
091
092    public void setWaveFormSelection(float waveFormSelection) {
093        this.waveFormSelection = waveFormSelection;
094    }
095
096    public float getSpreadRibbonPosition() {
097        return spreadRibbonPosition;
098    }
099
100    public void setSpreadRibbonPosition(float spreadRibbonPosition) {
101        this.spreadRibbonPosition = spreadRibbonPosition;
102    }
103
104    public float getNoiseAmount() {
105        return noiseAmount;
106    }
107
108    public void setNoiseAmount(float noiseAmount) {
109        this.noiseAmount = noiseAmount;
110    }
111
112    @NonNull
113    @Override
114    public String toString() {
115        return presetName;
116    }
117
118}
